  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Qsite provides an easy way for your customers to check their ticket status. The ticket status page shows a summary of the ticket, the current status of the ticket, the balance due, and when it was last updated.</p><h3 id=\"AddaQsite\u2122TicketStatusLinktoReceiptsandInvoices-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936425067/Qsite+Ticket+Status+-+Keep+Customers+Updated+on+Their+Tickets\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936425067\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qsite\u2122 Ticket Status</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523327/Qsite+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523327\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qsite\u2122 Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361958/Print+Settings+-+Receipt+Template\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932361958\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Print Settings - Receipts</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170710.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"AddaQsite\u2122TicketStatusLinktoReceiptsandInvoices-AddingQsiteLinkstoReceiptsandInvoices\">Adding Qsite Links to Receipts and Invoices</h2><p /><p>1. On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Settings</strong> \u2192 <strong>Location Settings</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170715.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. On the Settings Overview page, click the <strong>Templates</strong> dropdown on the left column. From the list of options, click either <strong>Receipts</strong> or <strong>Invoices</strong>, depending on which template you would like to change.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170721.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. On the Template Settings page, look for the <strong>Ticket Status URL</strong> section. Once you are satisfied with your changes, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170727.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p>Click the checkbox next to <strong>Show URL</strong> to print the Qsite portal URL on your receipt/invoice.</p></li><li><p>Click the checkbox next to <strong>Show QRcode</strong> to print a QR code with the Qsite portal URL on your receipt/invoice.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"AddaQsite\u2122TicketStatusLinktoReceiptsandInvoices-ShowURL\">Show URL</h3><p>This option adds a Qsite\u2122 ticket status portal link to the ticket receipt or invoice.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170742.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"AddaQsite\u2122TicketStatusLinktoReceiptsandInvoices-ShowQRCode\">Show QR Code</h3><p>\u00a0This option adds a Qsite\u2122 ticket status portal QR code link to the ticket receipt or invoice\u00a0that the customer can scan and follow from their smartphone.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936851011/image-20230608-170748.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
